{"tid":1023312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏] 報告：病歷恐成為中國勒索美國人的新武器","createTime":"2019-02-15T16:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T19:35:33.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c438c6aeb997aaeaa18f9d6979e6aeff9240a3ad","tid":1023312,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"報告：病歷恐成為中國勒索美國人的新武器<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6132139/article-%e5%a0%b1%e5%91%8a%ef%bc%9a%e7%97%85%e6%ad%b7%e6%81%90%e6%88%90%e7%82%ba%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%8b%92%e7%b4%a2%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e7%9a%84%e6%96%b0%e6%ad%a6%e5%99%a8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6132139%2Farticle-%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e5%2591%258a%25ef%25bc%259a%25e7%2597%2585%25e6%25ad%25b7%25e6%2581%2590%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%2582%25ba%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%258b%2592%25e7%25b4%25a2%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%259a%2584%25e6%2596%25b0%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e5%2599%25a8%2F&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=dddcbd6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6132139/article-%e5%a0%b1%e5%91%8a%ef%bc%9a%e7%97%85%e6%ad%b7%e6%81%90%e6%88%90%e7%82%ba%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%8b%92%e7%b4%a2%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e7%9a%84%e6%96%b0%e6%ad%a6%e5%99%a8/</a><br />\n<br />\n國會諮詢機構美中經濟暨安全審查委員會（USCC）提出的報告顯示，中國投資美國生技產業可能令美國的國安面臨風險，中國政府可能因此取得勒索美國人的病歷資料。<br />\n<br />\n彭博資訊報導，USCC在14日提出的報告中表示，中國生技公司透過投資美國企業、與美國大學合作、延攬美國研究人才等方式，已取得有關技術，並蒐集大量美國居民的臨床與基因資料。<br />\n<br />\n在美國國安方面，新法令已促使政府重視生技產業的程度不亞於航空航太與微晶片。而<span style=\"color: red;\">美國調查公司PitchBook的數據則顯示，去年至少有一名中國投資人參與美國41件生技產業集資案，籌資總額達到26億美元。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，理論上，中國取得美國人的私人資料可能帶來勒索風險，遭鎖定對象可能因此暴露健康狀況。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，報告仍表示，雖然中國是對美國個人就醫資料發動網攻的主要國家之一，但目前仍沒有證據表明北京將這類資料運用在「戰略、敵對等方面。」"},{"pid":"5094b703b86822ff46025b60a6f1d3933a41ed93","tid":1023312,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"支共真係人類毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37b8fc34b2c0aee0c3904a89c0a1181841f1d35","tid":1023312,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"生技？<br />\n死忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9085576d5b6654faba9b23b21bf4c3355fc00c65","tid":1023312,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T18:57:37.000Z","msg":"病歷資料可以點樣勒索?<br />\n目前我只諗到可能賣器官賺美金<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc544e8f0669f586a29878f62f8470d5798a1866","tid":1023312,"uid":19005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9085576d5b6654faba9b23b21bf4c3355fc00c65","tid":1023312,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T18:57:37.000Z","msg":"病歷資料可以點樣勒索?<br />\n目前我只諗到可能賣器官賺美金<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T19:33:45.000Z","msg":"攞人地資料就冇咩用<br />\n<br />\n佢攞嚟公開俾各國睇根本威脅"},{"pid":"cc90620b6fc6d5a81432248cfcfaf5adb25448b2","tid":1023312,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T19:35:33.000Z","msg":"某人：行得正企得正怕咩比人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}